content: Thank you so much for the limited edition offer to make the game free.I always thought that I wouldn't be able to get it but look at me now.Thank you so much.

I played hs days,college days,and the holiday sequels.The story is cute and interesting but why aren't there more new male characters in the group to interact with besides a psycho stalker (who seems to old to be a college student anyhow.) why when you pick who to use as your character there arent more male options.I always thought the option with the leather jacket and black and blue hair could be used as a he he would always be described as female.
